title: Throw back Thursday with SWV and Juvenile
itunes:title: Throw back Thursday with SWV and Juvenile
description:
Today on the show we flashed back to when we had the whole RnB group SWV stop by where they spoke about fan love, old relationships, the meaning of their songs and more. Also, we flashed back to the time Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to  a woman from New Orleans who used her ex's prosthetic leg to beat him up after he broke up with her. Also, we flashed back to when Angela helped some listeners out during "Ask Yee".
